                  <p className="text-[11px] text-neutral-400">­ƒÆ│ <strong>Cash & MoMo chaos</strong> ÔÇö fragmented payments that don't reconcile</p>
                  <p className="text-[11px] text-neutral-400">­ƒÅ¬ <strong>Owner trapped at the shop</strong> ÔÇö can't see what's happening without being there</p>
                </div>
